sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as app-admin / app-api-ts
    participant Connectors as app-connectors
    participant Vendor as Systeme source
    participant Store as payload store
    participant Worker as app-api worker
    participant DB as Postgres / integration_*

    Admin->>Connectors: issue ingest credentials
    Connectors-->>Admin: ingestUrl + apiKey + signingSecret?
    Vendor->>Connectors: POST /v1/ingest/:orgId/:connectionId/events
    Connectors->>Store: persist payload brut
    Connectors->>Connectors: create raw event summary
    Worker->>Connectors: claim raw events / read payload
    Connectors-->>Worker: metadata + payload brut
    Worker->>DB: ingest dataset/raw + mark processed
